---
import Nav from '../Nav.astro';
---

<div class="w-hero-wrapper">
  <canvas id="waveCanvas" aria-hidden="true"></canvas>
  <Nav />
  <div class="w-hero">
    <div class="w-hero-grid">
      <div class="w-hero-left">
        <p class="w-hero-eyebrow"><span class="w-glyph" aria-hidden="true">◇</span> Coming Soon</p>
        <h1>The complete weather SDK for prediction markets.</h1>
        <p class="w-hero-sub">Observations, forecasts, satellite, and settlement. All the data behind every Kalshi and Polymarket weather contract. Built for AI agents and&nbsp;quants.</p>
        <div class="w-hero-ctas">
          <a href="#early-access" class="w-btn">Join the waitlist</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="w-terminal">
        <div class="w-terminal-bar">
          <span class="live-dot" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          <span class="w-terminal-title">MOSTLY RIGHT SDK · PREVIEW</span>
        </div>
        <pre class="w-terminal-body">$ pip install mostlyright

<span class="w-term-muted">mostlyright 0.11.0 · ready</span>

Cities............<span class="w-term-num">60+</span>
History...........<span class="w-term-num">1948</span> → <span class="w-term-live">live</span>
Forecasts.........NBM · GFS · HRRR · ECMWF
Satellite.........GOES-16 + 19
Markets...........Kalshi · Polymarket
Market data.......candles · L2 books (full depth)
Settlement........NWS CLI (LST-aware)
Reconciliation....source-priority dedup
Precision.........T-group (decimal)
Output............TOON · pandas · polars · json

<span class="w-term-muted">$ _</span></pre>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
